@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "AboutUs";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/MasterPage_User.cshtml";
}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/CSS/AboutUsCSS.css" />

<div class="main-container">
    <h1 class="page-title">About SkyPath</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">
        Everything you need to know about the platform you’re using — how it works, what we store, and how we keep you informed.
    </p>

    <!-- FAQ Grid -->
    <div class="faq-section">
        <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">How can I find the cheapest flight using SkyPath?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    Find the cheapest time to fly. If you have a destination in mind and want to find the cheapest flight, simply select the
                    <strong>'sort by price: low to high'</strong> option during your search. This will help you find the cheapest day to fly.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">How does SkyPath work?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    We're a flight search engine. We scan all the top airlines and travel providers across the web, so you can compare airlines and other travel related costs – all in one place.
                    Once you've found the best flight, you can book directly with the provider.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">What happens after I book my flight?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    Your flight booking confirmation email and any additional information you need will come from the airline or supplier you booked with.
                    If you have any further questions about your booking, or if you want to change or cancel your flight, please contact them.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">Where should I book a flight to now?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    If you're looking for inspiration for your next trip, it's worth
                    <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=travel+destinations&oq=travel+destinatio&gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUqBwgCEAAYgAQyBwgAEAAYgAQyBggBEEUYOTIHCAIQABiABDIHCAMQABiABDIHCAQQABiABDIHCAUQABiABDIHCAYQABiABDIHCAYQABiABDIHCAcQABiABDIHCAgQABiABDIHCAkQABiABNIBCTE3MzAzajBqN6gCALACAA&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8">
                        searching the world
                    </a>
                    to find a cheap flight ticket to anywhere.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">Is it possible to book a flexible flight ticket?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    We understand how important it is to keep your vacation plans flexible. Sometimes, there may be an additional fee for a changeable flight ticket,
                    so it's a good idea to look for this option when booking.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">Should I book my flight through SkyPath?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    We are a search engine, so once you find the best flight ticket, you can book it directly through the airline or travel provider's website.
                    This way, you will have the opportunity to add any details you want about the customer and choose preferred flight options, such as seats.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Registered-only: How it works for you -->
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-title">How SkyPath Works for You</h2>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p>
                As a registered SkyPath user, you get more than flight search. Your account allows SkyPath to provide a smoother experience by keeping your activity connected to your profile.
            </p>

            <div class="feature-bullets">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-title">Faster browsing</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">Your searches and navigation flow are optimized for repeat usage.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-title">Personalized notifications</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">You can receive user-specific announcements and updates based on your account context.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-title">Better control</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">A registered account makes it easier to manage your experience across the site.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <ul class="policy-list">
                <li>Filter flights by departure/destination and time window</li>
                <li>Use sorting to quickly find best price or best schedule</li>
                <li>View company announcements and your personal notifications in one place</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Registered-only: Announcements and notifications -->
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-title">Announcements & Notifications</h2>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p>
                SkyPath uses announcements and notifications to keep you informed. There are two types:
            </p>
            <ul class="policy-list">
                <li><strong>Company announcements</strong> — updates that apply to everyone (maintenance, platform updates, new features).</li>
                <li><strong>My notifications</strong> — user-specific messages related to your account activity and relevant alerts.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                This is designed so you never miss important updates, but also don’t get overwhelmed by irrelevant information.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Registered-only: Data & privacy -->
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-title">Your Data & Privacy</h2>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p>
                We respect your privacy. Your account information is used only to support core site functionality (authentication, personalization, and user-specific features).
            </p>
            <ul class="policy-list">
                <li>We do not sell personal data.</li>
                <li>We only store what we need to operate the platform features.</li>
                <li>You can request removal of your data according to platform policy.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Optional: What’s next -->
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-title">What We’re Working On</h2>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p>
                SkyPath is evolving. Here are examples of improvements we aim to add over time:
            </p>
            <ul class="policy-list">
                <li>Saved flights and favorites</li>
                <li>Price alerts for specific routes</li>
                <li>More detailed flight comparisons</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Company Info -->
    <div class="company-info">
        <h2>Why Choose SkyPath?</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 30px;">
            We've been helping travelers find their perfect flights for over 15 years. Our commitment to transparency,
            competitive pricing, and exceptional customer service has made us the trusted choice for millions of travelers worldwide.
        </p>
        <div class="company-stats">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">50M+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Happy Travelers</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">200+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Destinations</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Partner Airlines</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Customer Support</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Child Safety Policy -->
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-title">Child Safety Policy</h2>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p>
                At our site, the safety and well-being of children are our top priority. We are committed to creating a secure and respectful online environment.
                We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13 without parental consent.
                Any content on our site is designed to be safe, inclusive, and appropriate for all users.
            </p>
            <p>
                If you believe a child has provided us with personal information without parental consent, please contact us immediately, and we will promptly remove the information.
            </p>
            <p>
                Your trust means everything to us, and we are dedicated to ensuring a safe and positive experience for all families who use our website.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Accessibility Statement -->
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-title">Accessibility Statement</h2>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p>
                At our site, we are committed to making our website accessible to everyone, including people with disabilities.
                Our goal is to provide an inclusive and user-friendly experience for all visitors.
            </p>
            <p>
                We strive to follow recognized accessibility standards and continuously work to improve our site's design and functionality.
            </p>
            <p>
                If you experience any difficulty accessing content on our website or have suggestions on how we can improve accessibility,
                please contact us at <a href="mailto:email@gmail.com">email@gmail.com</a>. We value your feedback and will do our best to address your concerns promptly.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
